#---------------------------------------------------
# |open folder|perms        |filename     |emulator
# |(separator)|size         |perms        |show terminal
# |file or dir|emulator     |size         |(separator)
# |file or dir|show terminal|emulator     |emulator
# |file or dir|emulator list|show terminal|show terminal
# |file or dir|             |emulator list|(separator)
# |file or dir|             |open folder  |emulator
# |file or dir|             |             |show terminal
# |file or dir|             |             |(separator)
# |file or dir|             |             |make playlist
